      {
         "text": "#### Probable location\n\nThe possible location of Shimashki is unknown, which does not mean that attempts have not been made to identify it. In his work, Hamidreza Qashqai mentions an initial attempt to locate it in the suburbs of Khorram-Abad, Iran, but this hypothesis was contested, suggesting it might be further west (<htcite0>).\n\nAmong the proposals, the hypothesis has also been raised that Anshan was the capital of Shimashki. On the other hand, some consider that it could be north of Anshan (<htcite1>).\n\nWhat is not in doubt, however, is its location in the present-day territory of Iran.",
         "source": [
            {
               "type": 1,
               "uuid": "fc080160-6845-4a2e-b21e-977f22434f63",
               "text": "Hamidreza Qashqai",
               "page": "pp. 4",
               "date_time": {
                  "type": "gregory",
                  "year": "2024",
                  "month": "",
                  "day": ""
               }
            },
            {
               "type": 1,
               "uuid": "fc080160-6845-4a2e-b21e-977f22434f63",
