      {
         "id": "11c9a5e9-29e3-4ee8-8d2a-fe763b39b049",
         "name": "Kings of Shimashki",
         "history": [
            {
               "text": "In this text, we will deal with the kings listed by Walther Hinz in his work (<htcite0>), which portrays the history of the kings of Shimashki in the period between <htdate0> and <htdate1>. However, the fact that we place them together does not indicate that they are from the same family.\n\nIn addition to the work of Walther Hinz, we will analyze the work of Hamidreza Qashqai (<htcite1>), which presents us with three additional kings. This divergence regarding the number of kings is even explained in the work of Hamidreza Qashqai, which mentions the possibility that the names of the kings are a combination of different lists (<htcite2>).",
               "source": [
